      "instruction": "<p><strong>Chop</strong> and discard the ends off the courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Using</strong> a peeler, peel the courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> lengthways down to the core to form a pile of courgette ribbons</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the ribbons to a pot, pour over enough boiled water (from the kettle) so they are fully submerged and set aside for 5 min</p>",
